          </a>
        </div>
      </div>

      <div class="hero-right">
        <h1 class="hero-greeting">HEY THERE,</h1>
        <p class="hero-bio">welcome to my website! I'm Judit Bekker, and I'm happy to have you here. I've been working as a Data Visualization Designer and Analyst for 15 years, and I'm obsessed with all things data. Whether I'm finding new ways to visualize complex information or digging into data to uncover insights, I'm always up to something. I tend to choose topics that need unique datasets, and if I'm married to an idea I don't mind spending a month working on a viz. Spoiler alert: I once counted all the damn fine coffees that were consumed in Twin Peaks, and those 50 hours flew by faster than a coffee gets cold.</p>
        <p class="hero-bio">When I'm not working, you can catch me doodling on photos, coming up with new hobbies, or running away from my arch enemies: pigeons. I'm excited to share my projects and knowledge with you on this new website where I can finally embrace my everlasting love for my favourite font: Futura!</p>
        <div class="hero-ctas">
          <a href="/about-me" class="btn-link">More About Me</a>
          <a href="#portfolio" class="btn-link">My Portfolio</a>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- Portfolio -->
  <section class="portfolio" id="portfolio">
    <div class="container">
      <h2 class="section-title">My Portfolio</h2>
      <p class="section-subtitle">Here you'll find a selection of my work, and soon realise that the majority of them are about movies and television. Click on the images to get to know more, and explore the interactive versions.</p>
      <div class="portfolio-grid">
        <a href="https://public.tableau.com/app/profile/judit.bekker/viz/TheCoffeesofTwinPeaks/TheCoffeesofTwinPeaks" target="_blank" rel="noopener" class="portfolio-item">
          <img src={`${import.meta.env.BASE_URL}images/portfolio/twin-peaks.png`} alt="The Coffees of Twin Peaks" />
        </a>
        <a href="https://public.tableau.com/app/profile/judit.bekker/viz/BeerhikinginBerlin/bierwandern" target="_blank" rel="noopener" class="portfolio-item">
          <img src={`${import.meta.env.BASE_URL}images/portfolio/beer-hiking.png`} alt="Beer hiking in Berlin" />
        </a>
        <a href="https://public.tableau.com/app/profile/judit.bekker/viz/Mostfamouscomposersofthe20thcentury/Composersofthe20thcentury" target="_blank" rel="noopener" class="portfolio-item">
          <img src={`${import.meta.env.BASE_URL}images/portfolio/composers.jpg`} alt="Most famous composers of the 20th century" />
        </a>
        <a href="https://www.behance.net/gallery/115499067/Whats-in-the-bag" target="_blank" rel="noopener" class="portfolio-item">
          <img src={`${import.meta.env.BASE_URL}images/portfolio/what-s-in-the-bag.png`} alt="What's in the bag?" />
        </a>
        <a href="https://public.tableau.com/app/profile/judit.bekker/viz/setmymindonFIRE/Firewalkwithme" target="_blank" rel="noopener" class="portfolio-item">
          <img src={`${import.meta.env.BASE_URL}images/portfolio/fire-walk-with-me.png`} alt="Fire Walk With Me" />
        </a>
        <a href="https://public.tableau.com/app/profile/judit.bekker/viz/Thehistoryofmodernphotography/Historyofmodernphotography" target="_blank" rel="noopener" class="portfolio-item">
          <img src={`${import.meta.env.BASE_URL}images/portfolio/kodak.jpg`} alt="The History of Modern Photography" />
        </a>
        <a href="https://public.tableau.com/app/profile/judit.bekker/viz/WildatHeart/WildatHeart" target="_blank" rel="noopener" class="portfolio-item">
          <img src={`${import.meta.env.BASE_URL}images/portfolio/wild-at-heart.png`} alt="Wild at Heart" />
        </a>
        <a href="https://public.tableau.com/app/profile/judit.bekker/viz/SeverancePleaseenjoyeachfactequally/Ahandshakeisavailableuponrequest" target="_blank" rel="noopener" class="portfolio-item">
          <img src={`${import.meta.env.BASE_URL}images/portfolio/severance.png`} alt="Please enjoy each fact equally (Severance)" />
        </a>
        <a href="https://www.behance.net/gallery/122698727/Amy-Adams-movies" target="_blank" rel="noopener" class="portfolio-item">
          <img src={`${import.meta.env.BASE_URL}images/portfolio/amy-adams.png`} alt="Amy Adams Career" />
        </a>
        <a href="https://www.behance.net/gallery/169433427/Largest-lakes-around-Berlin" target="_blank" rel="noopener" class="portfolio-item">
          <img src={`${import.meta.env.BASE_URL}images/portfolio/lakes-of-berlin.jpg`} alt="Lakes of Berlin" />
        </a>
        <a href="https://public.tableau.com/app/profile/judit.bekker/viz/IcelandTheLandofFireandIce/IcelandThelandoffireandice" target="_blank" rel="noopener" class="portfolio-item">
          <img src={`${import.meta.env.BASE_URL}images/portfolio/iceland.png`} alt="The Land of Ice and Fire" />
        </a>
        <a href="https://public.tableau.com/app/profile/judit.bekker/viz/moonpalace/Moonphases2020" target="_blank" rel="noopener" class="portfolio-item">
          <img src={`${import.meta.env.BASE_URL}images/portfolio/moon-phases.png`} alt="Moon Phases 2020" />
        </a>
        <a href="https://public.tableau.com/app/profile/judit.bekker/viz/EasternBloc-StalinistArchitecture/Eastern_bloc" target="_blank" rel="noopener" class="portfolio-item">
          <img src={`${import.meta.env.BASE_URL}images/portfolio/eastern-bloc.jpg`} alt="Eastern Bloc" />
        </a>
        <a href="https://public.tableau.com/app/profile/judit.bekker/viz/infinite_jest/InfiniteJest" target="_blank" rel="noopener" class="portfolio-item">
          <img src={`${import.meta.env.BASE_URL}images/portfolio/infinite-jest.png`} alt="Infinite Jest" />
        </a>
        <a href="https://public.tableau.com/app/profile/judit.bekker/viz/MyFallenKingdom/Fallenkingdom" target="_blank" rel="noopener" class="portfolio-item">
          <img src={`${import.meta.env.BASE_URL}images/portfolio/my-fallen-kingdom.png`} alt="My Fallen Kingdom" />
        </a>
        <a href="https://public.tableau.com/app/profile/judit.bekker/viz/WoodyAllenTheManfromNewYork/WoodyAllen" target="_blank" rel="noopener" class="portfolio-item">
          <img src={`${import.meta.env.BASE_URL}images/portfolio/woody-allen.png`} alt="Woody Allen's filmography" />
        </a>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

</Layout>

<style>
  .hero {
    padding: 64px 0 72px;
  }

  .hero-inner {
    display: grid;
    grid-template-columns: 260px 1fr;
    gap: 64px;
    align-items: start;
  }

  .hero-left {
    display: flex;
    flex-direction: column;
    align-items: flex-start;
    gap: 20px;
  }

  .hero-photo-wrap {
    width: 220px;
    height: 220px;
    overflow: hidden;
    border-radius: 4px;
  }

  .hero-photo {
    width: 100%;
    height: 100%;
    object-fit: cover;
  }

  .hero-meta {
    display: flex;
    flex-direction: column;
    gap: 4px;
    font-size: 0.85rem;
  }

  .hero-name {
    font-size: 1rem;
    font-weight: 700;
  }

  .social-links {
    display: flex;
    gap: 14px;
  }

  .social-links a {
    color: var(--color-text);
    transition: color 0.2s;
  }

  .social-links a:hover {
    color: var(--color-accent);
    text-decoration: none;
  }

  .hero-right {
    padding-top: 8px;
  }

  .hero-greeting {
    font-size: clamp(3rem, 6vw, 5.5rem);
    font-weight: 700;
    color: var(--color-accent);
    letter-spacing: -0.01em;
    margin-bottom: 24px;
    line-height: 1;
  }

  .hero-bio {
    font-size: 0.95rem;
    line-height: 1.7;
    max-width: 620px;
    margin-bottom: 16px;
  }

  .hero-ctas {
    display: flex;
    gap: 24px;
    margin-top: 28px;
  }

  .btn-link {
    font-size: 0.85rem;
    font-weight: 500;
    letter-spacing: 0.06em;
    text-transform: uppercase;
    color: var(--color-text);
    border-bottom: 2px solid var(--color-text);
    padding-bottom: 2px;
    text-decoration: none;
    transition: color 0.2s, border-color 0.2s;
  }

  .btn-link:hover {
    color: var(--color-accent);
    border-color: var(--color-accent);
    text-decoration: none;
  }

  .portfolio {
    padding: 64px 0 80px;
    border-top: 1px solid var(--color-border);
  }

  .section-title {
    font-size: 2rem;
    font-weight: 700;
    margin-bottom: 12px;
  }

  .section-subtitle {
    color: var(--color-muted);
    font-size: 0.9rem;
    max-width: 600px;
    margin-bottom: 40px;
  }

  .portfolio-grid {
    display: grid;
    grid-template-columns: repeat(auto-fill, minmax(280px, 1fr));
    gap: 20px;
  }

  .portfolio-item img {
    width: 100%;
    aspect-ratio: 4/3;
    object-fit: cover;
    transition: opacity 0.2s;
    border: 1px solid var(--color-border);
  }

  .portfolio-item:hover img {
    opacity: 0.85;
  }

  .portfolio-placeholder {
    color: var(--color-muted);
    font-size: 0.85rem;
    grid-column: 1 / -1;
  }

  .portfolio-placeholder code {
    background: #f5f5f5;
    padding: 1px 5px;
    border-radius: 3px;
    font-size: 0.8rem;
  }

  @media (max-width: 768px) {
    .hero-inner {
      grid-template-columns: 1fr;
      gap: 40px;
    }

    .hero-photo-wrap {
      width: 160px;
      height: 160px;
    }
  }
</style>
